        "management": "First-line: pelvic floor muscle training (PFMT) x 3-6 months. Lifestyle: weight loss, treat constipation, smoking cessation. Devices: vaginal pessaries, urethral inserts. Surgery: mid-urethral sling (retropubic or transobturator TVT/TOT) - gold standard. Colposuspension (Burch) if sling contraindicated."
