        ],
        "management": "Surgical: pubovaginal sling (autologous fascia), urethral bulking agents (collagen, carbon beads, Macroplastique). Adjustable continence therapy (ACT). Artificial urinary sphincter (AUS) - gold standard for severe ISD."
